ğŸ” CI/CD Flow

Click Fix & Redeploy

App sends event to GitHub:

repository_dispatch: fix


GitHub Actions:

Fixes broken config

Builds Docker image

Deploys service

App keeps checking status

When service is live â†’ UI updates

